# Employee Management API

A RESTful Employee Management API built using **Go (Golang)**. This project provides CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for managing employee records.

## Features

- Add a new employee
- Retrieve all employees
- Retrieve an employee by ID
- Update employee details
- Delete an employee
- JSON request and response format
- RESTful API design
- Modular project structure

## Tech Stack

- Go (Golang)
- net/http
- encoding/json
- REST API

## Project Structure

```
Employee/
│── controllers/
│   └── employee_controller.go
│
│── models/
│   └── employee.go
│
│── services/
│   └── employee_service.go
│
│── routes/
│   └── routes.go
│── .env
│── main.go
│── go.mod
│── go.sum
│── README.md
```